    "description": {
      "zh": "亨利连发武器公司制造的.357马格南口径杠杆式步枪。该步枪采用发蓝处理的钢制机匣，胡桃木枪托与前护木，配备10发内置管状弹仓及16.5英寸枪管，搭载可调节半鹿角式机械瞄具。",
      "en": "Lever-action rifle chambered for .357 Magnum, manufactured by Henry Repeating Arms. The rifle features a steel receiver with a blued finish, walnut stock and forearm, 10 round internal tube magazine, and a 16.5\" barrel with adjustable semi-buckhorn sights."
